[diminishing marginal product]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diminishing_returns
[efficient scale]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minimum_efficient_scale
[Average Total Cost]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Average_total_cost
[Marginal Cost]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marginal_cost
